      <div class="warn-box">
        ⚠️ <strong>This is NOT a sales campaign.</strong> Do not treat replies as sales leads unless the patient specifically expresses interest in continuing care or purchasing hearing aids.
      </div>
      <p>Two emails are sent automatically once the campaign is triggered. Your role is to monitor replies daily and move contacts to the correct pipeline stage based on their response.</p>

      <h3>Who Receives This Campaign</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Contacts tagged <code>true hearing</code> — approximately 96 contacts</li>
        <li>Contacts tagged <code>true hearing one year</code> — approximately 21 contacts</li>
        <li>Total: approximately <strong>117 patients</strong></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

