      <div class="step-row"><span class="step-num">2</span><p>Create a new Smart List — name it: <strong>True Hearing Patients — Transition 2026</strong></p></div>
      <div class="step-row"><span class="step-num">3</span><p>Set filters: <strong>Tags includes</strong> → <code>true hearing</code> AND/OR <strong>Tags includes</strong> → <code>true hearing one year</code></p></div>
      <div class="step-row"><span class="step-num">4</span><p>Click <strong>Save Smart List</strong></p></div>
      <div class="step-row"><span class="step-num">5</span><p>Select all contacts in the list — click <strong>"Select all X contacts"</strong></p></div>
      <div class="step-row"><span class="step-num">6</span><p>Click <strong>Actions → Add Tag</strong></p></div>
      <div class="step-row"><span class="step-num">7</span><p>Type <code>th_transition_2026</code> and confirm</p></div>
      <div class="step-row"><span class="step-num">8</span><p>Click <strong>Apply</strong> — the workflow fires automatically for every contact</p></div>

